1196
01:08:39,074 --> 01:08:40,784
Your father made you weak.

1197
01:08:40,867 --> 01:08:42,703
<b><font color="#ca6500">DICK:</font></b> <i>Careful, Damian.
He's drawing you in.</i>

1198
01:08:42,869 --> 01:08:44,329
<b><font color="#ca6500">DAMIAN:</font></b> <i>Stop fighting me.</i>

1199
01:08:44,413 --> 01:08:45,539
