1200
01:08:45,622 --> 01:08:47,165
<b><font color="#ca6500">DICK:</font></b> <i>We need to work together.</i>

1201
01:08:47,916 --> 01:08:50,210
<b><font color="#ca6500">DAMIAN:</font></b> <i>I will have control!</i> <b><font color="#00abfd">(GROANS)</font></b>

