<b><font color="#00abfd">(DAMIAN GRUNTS)</font></b>

1210
01:09:08,895 --> 01:09:09,855
<b><font color="#00abfd">(GROANS)</font></b>

1211
01:09:13,275 --> 01:09:15,319
- <b><font color="#00abfd">(DAMIAN GROANS)</font></b>
- <b><font color="#00abfd">(DICK CHUCKLES)</font></b>

1212
01:09:15,402 --> 01:09:17,946
Well, he'll have one hell of
a headache in the morning.

1213
01:09:18,030 --> 01:09:19,781
