I'm here to convince you.

1262
01:11:15,063 --> 01:11:17,607
Well, then convince away.

1263
01:11:18,692 --> 01:11:20,193
<b><font color="#00abfd">(EARTH-9 SUPERMAN GRUNTS)</font></b>

1264
01:11:26,241 --> 01:11:27,534
<b><font color="#00abfd">(BOTH STRAINING)</font></b>

1265
01:11:35,417 --> 01:11:36,543
<b><font color="#00abfd">(GROANS)</font></b>

1266
01:11:55,854 --> 01:11:56,980
<b><font color="#00abfd">(YELPS IN PAIN)</font></b>

1267
01:12:01,902 --> 01:12:03,278
<b><font color="#00abfd">(RUMBLING)</font></b>

1268
01:12:20,670 --> 01:12:22,214
<b><font color="#00abfd">(BOTH GRUNTING)</font></b>

1269
01:12:43,360 --> 01:12:44,486
Please stop.

1270
01:12:44,653 --> 01:12:46,279
You're tired and injured.

1271
01:12:48,114 --> 01:12:50,325
Not as injured as you're about to be.

1272
01:12:53,203 --> 01:12:54,204
You see...

1273
01:12:54,454 --> 01:12:55,580
I know your secret.

1274
01:12:56,164 --> 01:12:57,165
You're holding back.

1275
01:13:01,628 --> 01:13:02,879
You always held back.

1276
01:13:03,463 --> 01:13:04,464
We both used to.

1277
01:13:05,340 --> 01:13:06,800
But now I don't.

1278
01:13:07,801 --> 01:13:09,302
- <b><font color="#00abfd">(CHOKES)</font></b>
- Not anymore.

